# Canva Master Guide
**Outside Inn Studios | Thumbnail Production Reference**
*Last updated: April 2026 | Verified against live Canva session + canva.com documentation*

> This file exists so any AI assistant working with EIW has accurate, verified knowledge of Canva's capabilities and the correct thumbnail workflow. Do not give Canva advice without consulting this file first. Features and pricing verified April 2026.

---

## Why Canva (Not Figma)

Canva is the correct tool for EIW's thumbnail production. Figma is a layout tool — it cannot apply strokes or drop shadows that follow the actual shape of a person cutout. It always uses the rectangular bounding box. **This has been confirmed by direct testing.** Canva handles person-shaped outlines and shadows natively and correctly, as verified in a live session April 2026.

---

## Free vs. Pro — Complete Feature Reference

### ✅ Fully Free (No Pro Required)

| Feature | Notes |
|---|---|
| YouTube Thumbnail canvas (1280×720px) | Preset available, many free templates |
| Export as JPG or PNG | Standard quality, no watermark |
| Text effects (Shadow, Lift, Hollow, Splice, Outline, Echo, Glitch, Neon, Curve, Background) | All 10+ built-in text effects free |
| Drop shadow on images | Follows actual person shape, not rectangle — **verified** |
| Outline/stroke on images | Follows actual person shape, not rectangle — **verified** |
| Photo filters (presets) | Solar, Festive, Retro, Cali, Summer, Drama, Nordic, Epic, and more |
| Photo adjustments (manual sliders) | Brightness, contrast, saturation, warmth, tint, vibrance, fade, highlights, shadows, sharpness, clarity, vignette |
| Auto-adjust | One-click AI enhancement |
| Blur | Whole-image slider, selective brush blur, Auto Focus (blurs background, keeps subject sharp) |
| Duotone | Two-color overlay with intensity slider |
| Image recolor | Color Edit tool, element color tiles, adjustment sliders |
| Elements library (partial) | 3+ million free graphics, arrows, icons — filter by "Free" to avoid Pro elements |
| Face Retouch | Smoothes skin, brightens eyes |
| Liquify | Bloat, Pinch, Swirl distortion brushes |
| Auto Focus | Subject detection + background blur |
| Color Edit | Customizes highlights/shadows to match colors |
| Page Animations | Fade, Pop, Slide, Breathe, etc. |
| Element Animations | Animate specific elements, custom paths |
| QR Code Generator | Built-in |
| 5GB cloud storage | Per free account |
| 1 Brand Kit (3 colors only) | Basic branding |
| Up to 200 Standard AI uses or 20 Premium AI uses/month | Resets monthly |

### ❌ Pro Only (Requires Paid Plan)

| Feature | Why It Matters | Workaround |
|---|---|---|
| Background Remover (photo) | One-click AI cutout | Use **remove.bg** instead — better results anyway |
| Background Remover (video) | No free trial at all | No good free alternative |
| Magic Eraser | Paint over objects to remove them | Photopea (free, browser-based) |
| Magic Edit | AI generative fill/replace | No direct free equivalent |
| Transparent background export | PNG with transparency | Use remove.bg, then export from Canva with background color |
| Custom font uploads | Upload TTF/OTF files | Use Canva's 3,000+ built-in fonts (includes most Google Fonts) |
| Export quality/compression controls | Precise file size control | Standard export quality is fine for thumbnails |
| 100GB+ cloud storage | — | 5GB free is sufficient for thumbnails |
| Match and Move (Pro transitions) | Morphing slide transitions | Not relevant for thumbnail work |
| Magic Shortcuts (presentations) | C for confetti, B for blur, D for drumroll | Not relevant for thumbnail work |

### ⚠️ Partially Free (Important Nuance)

**Image outline on people:** The Outline effect in Shadows panel is free and follows the person shape. However, it only works correctly on images with a transparent background. Since Canva's Background Remover is Pro, you need to remove the background with remove.bg first, then upload to Canva. The outline effect itself is free — the workflow just requires the external tool.

**Elements library:** Millions of elements are free. Premium elements show a **crown icon (👑)**. Always filter by "Free" when searching Elements to avoid accidentally placing Pro assets that will export with a watermark.

**AI allowance:** Free accounts get up to 200 Standard AI uses or 20 Premium AI uses per month. This resets monthly. Most thumbnail workflows don't consume AI credits.

